  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There is limited data availability on effect of Metformin XR on 24-h plasma glucose, and
      there is no available data in chronic kidney disease (CKD). The planned study aims to provide
      data on glucose plasma level in relation to metformin plasma level in Diabetes Type II
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
