  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes patients aged between 18 and 80 years requiring metformin (and any
             other antidiabetic treatment)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy and lactation

          -  Hyperlactatemia (&gt; 2.5 mmol/L)

          -  No creatinine levels available since 3 months

          -  Severe hepatic insufficiency

          -  No liver function parameters available

          -  Need of investigation with iodized contrast media

          -  Hypersensitivity to metformin
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
